00:13:39.380 --> 00:13:40.539
make the Docker image available,

00:13:40.539 --> 00:13:42.200
get that image running in a container,

00:13:42.200 --> 00:13:43.140
get everything up and running

00:13:43.140 --> 00:13:45.739
so that we have access to our RStudio session.

00:13:45.739 --> 00:13:47.919
But once that initial startup is complete,

00:13:47.919 --> 00:13:49.419
that session is available

00:13:49.419 --> 00:13:52.460
and subsequent sessions will start much more quickly.

00:13:52.460 --> 00:13:54.940
And here we see this session didn't take too long

00:13:54.940 --> 00:13:56.239
to take it up and running.

