00:52:41.899 --> 00:52:44.060
Oh yeah, so when I,

00:52:44.060 --> 00:52:47.580
before I saw the RStudio launch in the studio lab

00:52:47.580 --> 00:52:50.820
in SageMaker, I started kind of building a workflow

