00:53:16.260 --> 00:53:18.580
Like if I'm comfortable using the R kernel

00:53:18.580 --> 00:53:21.939
in the native kind of Jupyter style environment,

00:53:21.939 --> 00:53:23.139
then I can do that.

00:53:23.139 --> 00:53:26.260
And I can interact with my environment that way.

